        <div class="faq-a">Tempest Marketing works exclusively with high-ticket businesses where a single qualified appointment directly translates to meaningful revenue. Our three core verticals are real estate professionals (agents, brokerages, investors), marketing and creative agencies selling monthly retainers, and B2B consultants or service firms with ticket sizes of $3,000 or more per engagement. This system is not designed for e-commerce, low-ticket consumer products, or businesses without an active or planned inbound lead source. If you are not currently running ads or do not have an inbound channel, we can build that as part of the Advanced Package.</div>
